PrecisOrder (a) authorizing CENTRAL VERMONT RAILWAY, INC. to sell its assets to THE NEW ENGLAND CENTRAL RAILROAD COMPANY, and (b) approving the entry by the CANADIAN NATIONAL RAILWAY COMPANY into an AGREEMENT with THE NEW ENGLAND CENTRAL RAILROAD COMPANY which will allow the latter to run its trains over the CN line between East Alburg, Vermont, and Montreal, Quebec.
